title: 156 - Dung Beatle Juice
description: On todays show the boys catch up on each others lives and chat about the latest shows they've been watching as they wait for Connor to finish Lokie. The guys then jump right into the Pod FOD to discuss all things across the internet. The boys discuss Drake's new 400,000 dollar mattress, Cicadas taking over, and Mitt gives an RIP to his favorite internet monkey George. The boys end feel Good Friday with a mad lib read by non other than the Lou Holtz. Be sure to subscribe to YouTube.com/thepodpmi to watch full episodes of the show, and keep sending your submissions and questions to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you all for listening ], well see you Wednesday.
